SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
~~~~~~~~~~~~~`~~~~~
"Phuk The World" was created on an un-expanded Amiga 1200.
The game has been tested only on an Amiga 1200.
Please note the this game requires nearly 2MB Chip to load because all the
code, music, sound FX and grafix are pre-loaded so there's no more disc
access needed throughout the game ( unless you save/load games! )
I have attempted to degrade the game so that it will work on a 1 mb
machine but with no success - The game map is to big and has too much
graphics !!

If you are having trouble getting "Phuk The World" to run on your set-up
then contact me at the address at the end of this doc or at the address on
the 'Info' page in the game.

