  FIRE BUTTON  - - - - - - > OOO  Up          |
  This activites         |   OOO   ^          |
  the invetory window    |         |          |
  so you can select      |         +          |
  wether to drop,pick    | Left<--+++-->Right |
  or use an object       |         +          |
