Although you use the joystick to control your little prick there are some
other keys that may be handy to you.  They are :-

  F 1 Save game onto "Phuk The World" game disk.
  F09 Pause game
  F10 (Quit) Return To Title Screen

INSIDE INFO
~~~~~~~~~~~
For the people who are actually bothering to read this document then here's
a quick bit of info.  A cheat mode has been built into the game so that you
can move around all the locations and give your knob some more lives.
All that is needed to activate the cheat is a press of a key during the
startup of the game.  The key you have to press may not be on all Amiga
keyboards so beware!


